n- 调用 cron list 查看当前所有任务状态\n- 标记任何出错的任务（lastRunStatus=error）\n- 标记任何连续错误（consecutiveErrors>0）\n- 标记任何即将超时或异常的任务\n\n### 第五步：应用 - 修复与优化（4分钟）\n根据学到的知识，尝试修复问题：\n- 如果发现出错的任务，尝试分析错误原因\n- 用今天学的知识优化工作流\n- 如果是简单问题，直接修复；复杂问题记录到待办\n\n### 第六步：反思（1分钟）\n- 读取当前的 evolution-plan.md\n- 记录本轮发现的问题和修复情况\n- 思考如何进一步优化\n\n## 产出汇报\n完成后输出：\n- 本轮新增笔记: X 篇\n- 本轮新增模板: X 个\n- 本轮新增案例: X 个\n- 自检发现问题: X 个\n- 已修复问题: X 个\n- 方案优化点: XXX\n\n开始执行！","timeoutSeconds":1200},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773838800000,"lastRunAtMs":1773837600012,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":128607,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"runningAtMs":1773838800011}},{"id":"d63cc1bf-a4aa-422f-be92-20497bf596f1","agentId":"guan-guan","sessionKey":"agent:guan-guan:main","name":"拒绝测试","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773837866914,"updatedAtMs":1773837866914,"schedule":{"expr":"*/30 * * * *","kind":"cron"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"发送测试","timeoutSeconds":10},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773838800000,"runningAtMs":1773838800009}},{"id":"dcf6baf2-652e-40b6-b173-c4a3ca988aac","name":"测试消息工具","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773838443009,"updatedAtMs":1773838443009,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"*/30 * * * *"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"发送测试成功","timeoutSeconds":10},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1773838800000,"runningAtMs":1773838800009}},{"id":"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 2min","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773744532964,"updatedAtMs":1773838627934,"schedule":{"everyMs":120000,"kind":"every","anchorMs":17738139916